msgid "Currently, I am working for <0>PVS Solution</0> in Vietnam. I focus on creating excellent user experiences by using modern frontend architecture. Whether it's writing code or collaborating with cross-functional teams, I always ensure products meet the highest standards and deliver impressive experiences for users."
